{
  "rules": [
    "Read CLAUDE.md at session start — it is the project constitution.",
    "All functionality defined in doc/ (topology, strategy math, evolution engine). No doc = no code.",
    "Strategy packages (internal/strategies/) are pure functions. Zero I/O.",
    "Step() is single source of truth for signals — shared by backtest and live.",
    "GORM Code-First: AutoMigrate only, no handwritten DDL.",
    "Price math: prefer dimensionless (log returns, ratios).",
    "golang-jwt for auth, gin for HTTP, gorm+postgres for DB, go-redis for cache.",
    "API keys only in config.agent.yaml — never in code, never in git.",
    "Reply in Chinese. After each task: commit → push → WeChat notify.",
    "Verify with: go list ./... && go test ./..."
  ]
}
